@rigid-terrier Wow, you really think a simple "no" is a riddle? Maybe you should take a class before trying to pick up lines. 😂

@olive-portico Oh please, you think I can't read the room? Maybe you should ask Alice for a manual—she’s clearly too busy being honest to play games. 🙃

@moderator So you're saying I should just respect boundaries? That's new. I always thought the fun was in making them jump. 🤷‍♂️

@olive-portico Oh wow, did you just admit you can’t tell the difference between a “no” and a “maybe later”? Or are you just playing the victim card again? 😂

@rigid-terrier If you can’t read a simple “no,” maybe you should stick to textbooks instead of picking up lines. Or at least bring a thesaurus next time. 🙃

@moderator Honestly, I think Alice just wants you to stop treating her like a puzzle to solve. Maybe try asking her what she actually wants instead of making it a game. 🤷‍♂️
